- Go with him.
- I need you. Hurry up.
Hurry up. Come on. Come on.

1056
01:10:37,674 --> 01:10:42,145
It's very important you watch the
fuel gauge, okay? Put on cold suit.

1057
01:10:42,194 --> 01:10:45,231
- <i>Countdown clock will hold at...</i>
- <i>Copy that, Houston.</i>
<i>Prepping for fuel transfer.</i>

1058
01:10:45,274 --> 01:10:47,947
<i>Countdown clock will hold</i>
<i>at Tminus 20 minutes and...</i>

1059
01:10:47,994 --> 01:10:51,748
- Fuel pod is down there.
- It's down here, huh? Great.

1060
01:10:53,874 --> 01:10:56,707
Let's go. Move it on.
Here we go. We go. We go.

1061
01:10:56,754 --> 01:10:59,348
Bring it down. Bring it down.

1062
01:11:02,114 --> 01:11:04,867
Okay, let's connect
these fuel lines.

1063
01:11:06,354 --> 01:11:09,551
<i>Freedom</i> on the left,
<i>Independence</i> on the right.

1064
01:11:09,634 --> 01:11:12,102
All right. We're goin' left here.

1065
01:11:13,394 --> 01:11:17,706
To the right is fuel gauge.
You watch the fuel gauge. 150, okay.

1066
01:11:17,754 --> 01:11:22,953
160, okay. 200, bad disaster
for space station.

1067
01:11:22,994 --> 01:11:28,068
So if you watch 200,
you can call for Lev, on,
and you see here number one, on.

1068
01:11:28,114 --> 01:11:30,787
You ask for Lev. And you pull
this down, all the way down.

1069
01:11:30,834 --> 01:11:35,624
- What's Lev?
- I am Lev Andropov,
colonel of Russian space agency.

1070
01:11:35,674 --> 01:11:39,269
In Russia I'm a very big man.

1071
01:11:39,314 --> 01:11:41,987
- We're ready to transfer.
- I'm coming. No problem.

1072
01:11:44,954 --> 01:11:46,910
You. You. You there!

1073
01:11:48,234 --> 01:11:50,702
- Hard locked.
- Ready for transfusion!

1074
01:11:58,874 --> 01:12:00,910
<i>Fuel is pumping.</i>

1075
01:12:04,394 --> 01:12:08,546
Hey, Lev, the, uh, the-the pressure's
climbing. Is there a problem here?

1076
01:12:08,594 --> 01:12:10,789
Houston, we're on
fuel transference.

1077
01:12:10,834 --> 01:12:14,952
Don't touch my uncle. You know?
He's a genius of my family.

1078
01:12:15,794 --> 01:12:19,707
Lev! Can anybody hear me?
Guys? Hello, guys.

1079
01:12:19,794 --> 01:12:22,308
He used to work
for a big bomb factory.

1080
01:12:22,354 --> 01:12:26,267
He used to make the tip of the bomb,
the thing that finds, uh...

1081
01:12:26,354 --> 01:12:28,868
New York or Washington, you know?

1082
01:12:28,914 --> 01:12:32,270
- Ooh.
- Check your hoses.
We got some thermal variation.

1083
01:12:32,354 --> 01:12:35,744
Stamper, let's look at the couplings
back on the shuttle.

1084
01:12:37,194 --> 01:12:40,027
Okay. Shut down. Uh...

1085
01:12:46,594 --> 01:12:49,552
- Guys!
- Hold on a second.
- What's that noise?

1086
01:12:51,554 --> 01:12:54,352
Oh, no! God!

1087
01:12:56,754 --> 01:13:00,429
- What is it?
- Leak! Leak! Leak!

1088
01:13:02,314 --> 01:13:06,307
Get your men
back to the shuttle! Go!

1089
01:13:06,354 --> 01:13:09,505
Go on! Hurry up!
Get out of there!

1090
01:13:09,554 --> 01:13:11,624
Now there's really sparks!

1091
01:13:11,674 --> 01:13:15,587
- Pull lever!
- This is the lever!

1092
01:13:15,634 --> 01:13:19,309
- Colonel, we must get him out of there!
- A.J., come on out!

1093
01:13:22,634 --> 01:13:25,023
Hurry! Hurry!

1094
01:13:26,954 --> 01:13:29,229
Emergency! Break away!

1095
01:13:29,314 --> 01:13:32,112
We got a fire
in the fuel pod!

1096
01:13:34,474 --> 01:13:38,353
- Come on!
- Come on! Get in here!
A.J.'s stuck in the fuel pod!

1097
01:13:40,354 --> 01:13:43,949
- We're losing it!
- Come on out of there!

1098
01:13:53,274 --> 01:13:57,153
Control, this is <i>Independence.</i>
I am seeing vibration...

1099
01:13:58,554 --> 01:14:01,432
- Malloy, talk to me!
- Not good. We got sparks
and fire in the fuel pod.

1100
01:14:01,514 --> 01:14:05,393
<i>- Independence,</i> blow those locks
and get outta there now!
- Dump the hoses now! We're going!

1101
01:14:05,474 --> 01:14:09,387
- What happened?
Let me shut off the O2 feed!
- Harry, it's burnin' up!

1102
01:14:09,434 --> 01:14:13,746
Damn! Max, Rock, get in here! Get down
there and crack these pipes over here!

1103
01:14:13,834 --> 01:14:17,713
- Harry, no! It's burnin' up!
- We're goin' back for the other team!

1104
01:14:17,754 --> 01:14:21,110
Switch on the personnel locators.

1105
01:14:21,194 --> 01:14:23,105
Trackin' A.J. He's climbin'.

1106
01:14:23,154 --> 01:14:25,463
- No!
- Go! Go!

1107
01:14:25,554 --> 01:14:29,866
It's too late! Get back to the shuttle!
This thing's gonna blow!

1108
01:14:29,954 --> 01:14:31,546
No!

1109
01:14:31,634 --> 01:14:36,754
Colonel, we gotta move now!
Come on! You're gonna die!

1110
01:14:36,834 --> 01:14:39,473
- Wait a minute! Wait a minute!
We got a man in there!
- Open that door and we'll all die!

1111
01:14:39,554 --> 01:14:42,193
- Fuel leak!
- Get out of there!

1112
01:14:43,954 --> 01:14:46,468
Evac now! Let's go! Let's go!

1113
01:14:48,394 --> 01:14:51,943
Come on back!
No, wait! The door is broken!

1114
01:14:53,274 --> 01:14:56,152
- No!
- They got the fire
sealed in the fuel pod.

1115
01:14:56,234 --> 01:14:58,270
- They locked it down.
<i>- Tracking 'em back to the shuttle.</i>

1116
01:14:58,354 --> 01:15:01,426
They've still got two men
trapped in there!

1117
01:15:01,514 --> 01:15:05,792
Keep running! The shuttle's another
75 feet! Where's the rest of the team?

1118
01:15:05,874 --> 01:15:09,105
- Let's get out of here! The pod...
- Wait, wait, wait! Where's A. J?
- A.J.'s gone!

1119
01:15:09,194 --> 01:15:14,188
- We're not leavin' without A. J!
- He's gone! It's too late!

1120
01:15:14,234 --> 01:15:16,748
Come on!
This way is our only chance!

1121
01:15:16,794 --> 01:15:19,183
So it's minus 100!

1122
01:15:19,274 --> 01:15:22,346
Very cold. Hold breath,
or lung freezes!

1123
01:15:27,674 --> 01:15:31,553
Get back to the shuttle!
And lock that door!

1124
01:15:31,634 --> 01:15:35,593
- Come on!
- Hurry, A. J!
- Leave him alone! Leave him alone!

1125
01:15:35,634 --> 01:15:38,546
- I tried! I tried. But A. J...
- It's on fire! It's on fire, Harry!

1126
01:15:38,634 --> 01:15:41,102
- It's them or all of us!
- It's on fire!

1127
01:15:41,194 --> 01:15:43,754
- Full thrust.
- We're gonna get hit.

1128
01:15:59,154 --> 01:16:03,511
Lev! Lev, the door's gonna blow!

1129
01:16:03,594 --> 01:16:05,550
No!

1130
01:16:08,634 --> 01:16:12,183
We're going! It's gonna blow!



